Params: {1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory79.jpg'}
{3: 'I found myself in a strange place after entering the game. I took a few steps around, and realized this must be the spawn point of this game.'}
{3: "I didn't see anyone around, but Kamui mentioned we would be playing in teams."}
{3: 'I anxiously opened the menu and selected the Member section.'}
{2: 'System', 3: 'Character: 【kuroname】. Team members: Vera, Camu, Karenina.'}
{3: 'I was shocked when I saw their names.'}
{3: 'Never thought I would be forming a team with them.'}
{2: 'What!?', 3: '1000', 4: 'Not even one Gray Raven?', 5: '1000'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: "What's up? You got a problem?", 4: '1'}
{3: 'It was Karenina.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Vera', 3: "I didn't see this coming...", 4: '2'}
{3: 'Vera came from the right. She was dragging her blade on the ground, making a clinking sound.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Camu', 3: 'You took so long.', 4: '3'}
{3: 'Camu also jumped out from the left.'}
{3: 'They walked to a position and stopped, then formed a regular triangle around me, still wearing their summer Coatings.'}
{3: 'I looked at the system notifications. These outfits seemed to be the default "hero\'s attire" generated by the system data.'}
{2: 'Did you have to rehearse for this entrance?', 3: '16', 4: 'Aloha?', 5: '18'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: 'What rehearsal? They were just copying me!', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Still impressive though.'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: '...Did you hit your head?', 4: '1'}
{3: "I actually liked that line. Too bad she didn't."}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: "Enough stupid jokes. Now that the last member is here, let's hurry up and head to the castle.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Vera', 3: "True. Speaking of which, Karenina, you went for scouting, didn't you? Did you see any castle? We have to go there for the King, right?", 4: '2'}
{2: 'What castle?', 3: '22', 4: 'Were you all here earlier than me?', 5: '23'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: "That's our main quest objective. This must be another of those role-playing games, where we need to take a quest from the King and defeat the Demon King.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Vera', 3: 'About ten minutes. Constructs seemed to load the game faster. Now Gray Raven will probably be ahead of us.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Camu', 3: "That's why we must hurry. I don't want to lose to that fool.", 4: '3'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: 'I went for scouting, but not for the castle.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Vera', 3: 'What did you do then?', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: "To find the other team and kill them, of course. If we spawned nearby, they shouldn't be too far away.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Vera', 3: "Wow... I didn't expect that. How did you go?", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: 'Nothing, duh. I came back empty-handed. Do I have to explain everything to you?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Vera', 3: 'No. I just want to hear you admit your failure.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: 'You red-haired ****... ', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Camu', 3: 'Stop it! Enemies have heard us!', 4: '3'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: 'Screw the enemies. I have more important things to do now!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Vera', 3: 'Oh can you?', 4: '2'}
{3: "Seeing there was nothing he could do to stop those two, Camu let out a roar, threw his greatsword away and charged toward the enemies, while Karenina was falling for Vera's taunt."}
{2: 'Demon', 3: 'Beep! Beep! Beep!'}
{3: 'It was a complete chaos.'}
{3: 'Only one word could describe my feeling at the moment.'}
{3: 'Hopeless.'}
